# UI Testing Snapshots

This directory stores Playwright visual regression test snapshots.

## Directory Structure

```
ui-snapshots/
├── {route}/           # e.g., dashboard, sprint, agent, etc.
│   ├── chromium/      # Chromium browser snapshots
│   │   ├── latest.png # Latest screenshot
│   │   └── ...        # Previous versions (auto-pruned to 5)
│   ├── firefox/
│   │   └── latest.png
│   └── webkit/
│       └── latest.png
```

## Retention Policy

- Keep maximum 5 versions per route/browser combo
- Auto-prune on each CI run
- `.gitkeep` tracks directory (snapshots are gitignored)

## Usage

See `docs/UI-TESTING-AUTOMATION.md` for full testing guide.
